---
title: The Manager's Cycle
---

flowchart TD

    A([Observe the Match])

    B[Identify the Problem]

    C[Gather Evidence]

    D[Form a Hypothesis]

    E[Make One Tactical Change]

    F[Observe the Next Phase]

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F -. Continuous Improvement .-> A

    classDef start fill:#2E5AAC,color:#ffffff,stroke:#1F3D6D,stroke-width:2px
    classDef process fill:#E8F0FB,color:#1F2937,stroke:#2E5AAC,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef feedback fill:#FFF8DC,color:#333333,stroke:#D4A017,stroke-width:1.5px

    class A start
    class B,C,D,E process
    class F feedback